lead_paragraph: Veteran forward Vedad Ibisevic scored twice, taking his career tally of Bundesliga goals to 100, only to get himself sent off as Hertha Berlin beat Mainz 05 2-1 on Sunday to go third.

headline.print_headline: Ibisevic Reaches 100 Bundesliga Goals, Sent Off in Hertha Win
headline.main: Ibisevic Reaches 100 Bundesliga Goals, Sent Off in Hertha Win
